<br aria-hidden="true">If you have an existing subscription to HBO Max that is billed directly by HBO Max, you will need to replace it with your Netflix &amp; HBO Max (With Ads) perk when you register HBO Max as part of your Netflix &amp; HBO Max (With Ads) perk. You will continue to be charged separately for any existing HBO Max account until you replace that account with your Netflix &amp; HBO Max (With Ads) perk.
<br aria-hidden="true">
<br aria-hidden="true">If you have an existing subscription to HBO Max that is billed by a third party, your Netflix &amp; HBO Max (With Ads) perk will not automatically replace that subscription and must be managed separately with that third-party provider.
<br aria-hidden="true">
