<br aria-hidden="true">Verizon will share your mobile telephone number and/or email address with HBO Max to facilitate your registration of the HBO Max service included in your Netflix &amp; HBO Max (With Ads) perk. For further information about how Verizon handles your personal data, please visit the Privacy Notice available on <a target="_blank" href="/home/internet/5g/privacy/" tabindex="-1">verizon.com/privacy</a>.
