<section class="u-colorBackgroundSecondary u-colorPrimary">
  <div class="Container u-marginBottom--0">
    <div class="cmp-accordion Col Col--12 u-colorBackgroundSecondary u-colorPrimary" data-dynamic="https://www.verizon.com/support/spot/?tag=5ghomeinternet&amp;amp;amp;count=30&amp;amp;amp;t=1589217688376">
      <h2 class="cmp-accordion-header u-textCenter u-textxsCenter u-fontDisplay u-textLineHeightTight u-text--40 u-text--md48 u-text--lg64 u-marginBottom--48">

        <span class="u-screenReaderOnly">
          Have questions? We’ve got answers.
        </span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">
            Have questions?
<br aria-hidden="true">We’ve got answers.
          </span>
      </h2>
      <div class="cmp-accordion-items u-colorPrimary">
        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        Is Frontier becoming Verizon?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Frontier is now a Verizon company, bringing better value and more choices to millions more customers across the country. By integrating Frontier's complementary pure-play fiber network with Verizon's industry-leading Fios and mobility assets, the company now has an expanded reach of almost 30 million fiber passings across 31 states and Washington, D.C. With the greater availability of premium home internet and mobility services, <a href="/home/internet/5g/articles/home/verizon-acquires-frontier/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p1||||||Is Frontier becoming Verizon?|customers have exclusive access&quot;}">customers have exclusive access</a> to new services, savings and value they can't get anywhere else. This expansion includes plan offerings for fiber optic home internet, fiber optic business internet, landline phones, and Fios TV.</p>
<p>See if you're eligible for fiber home internet by <a href="https://frontier.com/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p2||||||Is Frontier becoming Verizon?|checking availability&quot;}">checking availability</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        I'm a Verizon 5G Home customer. Will my internet options change now that Frontier is a Verizon company?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Current 5G Home Internet (and LTE Home Internet) customers do not need to take any action to continue their Verizon internet services. However, Frontier Fiber may be available at your current address. <a href="https://frontier.com/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p3||||||I'm a Verizon 5G Home customer. Will my internet options change now that Frontier is a Verizon company?|Check availability&quot;}">Check availability</a> to see if fiber internet is available in your area.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        What is Verizon 5G Home internet?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Verizon 5G Home Internet is a fast,* reliable home internet service that's based on the same <a href="/home/internet/5g/5g/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p4||||||What is Verizon 5G Home internet?|Verizon 5G Ultra Wideband&quot;}">Verizon 5G Ultra Wideband</a> network your mobile phone uses so you can game, stream and connect the way you want.</p>
<p>Unlike traditional cable internet, which uses copper wires, Verizon 5G Home Internet uses cellular communications (Verizon's 5G Ultra Wideband) to provide fast* home internet speeds with low lag.</p>
<p><b>How it works:</b> A 5G receiver in your home connects to signals from nearby 5G cell towers. The receiver acts as both modem and router, so all of your home devices can then connect to the 5G Ultra Wideband network through the router's Wi-Fi signal.</p>
<p>With Verizon 5G Home Internet, you'll enjoy:</p>
<ul>
<li>Reliable bandwidth to connect your home’s many devices</li>
<li>No annual contracts, extra fees or equipment charges</li>
<li>Affordable pricing with discounts like Auto Pay and when you combine it with any Verizon mobile phone plan</li>
<li>Competitive price guarantees on all plans</li>
<li>A credit of up to $500 to help cover early termination fees when you switch to Verizon 5G Home Internet</li>
<li>Easy plug-and-play setup**</li>
</ul>
<p>Because Verizon <a href="/home/internet/5g/5g/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p5||||||What is Verizon 5G Home internet?|5G Ultra Wideband&quot;}">5G Ultra Wideband</a> is now available in more and more places around the country, it's easier than ever to experience the speed and power of this home internet option. To check availability in your area, <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p6||||||What is Verizon 5G Home internet?|enter your address&quot;}">enter your address</a> or search our <a href="/home/internet/5g/coverage-map/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p7||||||What is Verizon 5G Home internet?|coverage map&quot;}">coverage map</a>.</p>
<p><span class="support-footnote">*5G Home and Verizon Home Internet Lite services provided through cellular network; speeds vary due to factors affecting cellular networks.</span></p>
<p><span class="support-footnote">**Self setup not available in all areas.</span></p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Because it's powered by our 5G Ultra Wideband network, Verizon 5G Home Internet is widely available across the US, from <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/near-me/seattle-washington/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p8||||||Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?|Seattle&quot;}">Seattle</a> and <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/near-me/new-orleans-louisiana/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p9||||||Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?|New Orleans&quot;}">New Orleans</a> to <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/near-me/cleveland-ohio/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p10||||||Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?|Cleveland&quot;}">Cleveland</a> and <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/near-me/indianapolis-indiana/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p11||||||Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?|Indianapolis&quot;}">Indianapolis</a>. With Verizon 5G Home Internet, it's easier than ever to experience the speed and power of broadband at home.</p>
<p>That said, not all areas that have 5G Ultra Wideband cellular service currently have access to Verizon 5G Home Internet. But Verizon's 5G network is expanding, with new locations added regularly. To check <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/fios-fastest-internet/availability/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p12||||||Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?|5G Home Internet availability&quot;}">5G Home Internet availability</a> in your area, enter <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p13||||||Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?|your address&quot;}">your address</a> or check out our <a href="/home/internet/5g/coverage-map/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p14||||||Where is Verizon 5G Home Internet available?|coverage map&quot;}">coverage map</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        How much does Verizon 5G Home Internet cost?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Your Verizon 5G Home Internet price will depend on which services are available at your address and which plan best fits your needs. All Verizon 5G Home Internet plans come with no annual contracts and no hidden fees, and a router is included at no extra charge for as long as you have your plan. Plus, with Verizon's Price-Lock Guarantee, you get a multi-year price guarantee (varies by plan), so you don't have to worry about unexpected price hikes.</p>
<p>You may also be eligible for <a href="/home/internet/5g/discounts/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p15||||||How much does Verizon 5G Home Internet cost?|Verizon discounts&quot;}">Verizon discounts</a> to help you save on our best home internet plans available in your area. You also can get a discount by <a href="/home/internet/5g/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p16||||||How much does Verizon 5G Home Internet cost?|bundling mobile and home&quot;}">bundling mobile and home</a> or by signing up for <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/auto-pay-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p17||||||How much does Verizon 5G Home Internet cost?|Auto Pay&quot;}">Auto Pay</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        How fast is Verizon 5G Home Internet?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Verizon 5G Home Internet speed is fast* enough for all the online activities you love: You can stream, game and video chat with low lag and buffering. Your 5G Home Internet speed will vary and depends on which plan you pick:</p>
<ul>
<li>5G Home: This plan provides fast, reliable download speeds capable of 1080p HD video streaming and Verizon's 3-year price-lock guarantee.</li>
<li>5G Home Plus: Enjoy unlimited premium data** with up to 150 Mbps download speeds and Verizon's 4-year price-lock guarantee, so you don't have to worry about unexpected rate hikes.</li>
<li>5G Home Ultimate: Offering unlimited premium data** our fastest speeds, this plan gives you the ability to stream shows and movies in brilliant Ultra HD 4K resolution and Verizon's 5-year price-lock guarantee.</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="support-footnote">*5G Home and Verizon Home Internet Lite services provided through cellular network; speeds vary due to factors affecting cellular networks.</span></p>
<p><span class="support-footnote">**Consumer data usage is subject to the usage restrictions set forth in Verizon's terms of service; visit: <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/customer-agreement/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p18||||||How fast is Verizon 5G Home Internet?|https://www.verizon.com/support/customer-agreement/&quot;}">https://www.verizon.com/support/customer-agreement/</a> for more information about 5G Home Internet or Verizon Home Internet Lite or <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/fios-customer-agreement/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p19||||||How fast is Verizon 5G Home Internet?|https://www.verizon.com/support/fios-customer-agreement/&quot;}">https://www.verizon.com/support/fios-customer-agreement/</a> for Fios internet.</span></p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        What is the difference between Verizon 5G Home Internet plans?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Verizon 5G Home Internet is a wireless connection powered by Verizon's 5G Ultra Wideband. All of Verizon's 5G Home Internet plans—5G Home, 5G Home Plus and 5G Home Ultimate—offer a fast,* reliable connection for everyone in your home so you can stream, work and game. Here are a few things to consider about Verizon 5G Home, 5G Home Plus and 5G Home Ultimate.</p>
<p>The <b>5G Home</b> plan includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>Plug-and-play Verizon Internet Gateway router</li>
<li>A credit of up to $500 to cover termination fees when you switch from another provider</li>
<li>A 30-day Money Back Guarantee</li>
<li>Our Price-Lock Guarantee, locking in your base rate for 3 years with no unexpected price hikes</li>
<li>1080p HD video streaming</li>
<li>Download speeds of up to 100 Mbps</li>
</ul>
<p>With <b>Verizon 5G Home Plus</b>, you get all the benefits of 5G Home Internet, as well as:</p>
<ul>
<li>Unlimited premium data,** with bandwidth for streaming, browsing, gaming and more</li>
<li>Our Price-Lock Guarantee, locking in your base rate for 4 years with no unexpected price hikes</li>
<li>Download speeds of up to 150 Mbps</li>
</ul>
<p><b>Verizon 5G Home Ultimate</b> is designed for homes with more devices and for those needing the fastest connection speeds. If you love to stream in crystal-clear 4K resolution, have a variety of smart devices or are a big gamer, it offers the bandwidth you need to power your entire home. You'll also get:</p>
<ul>
<li>Whole-Home Wi-Fi, including an optional extender to improve coverage in every room of your home</li>
<li>Unlimited premium data** for browsing, gaming and more</li>
<li>Ultra HD 4K video streaming</li>
<li>Our Price-Lock Guarantee, locking in your base rate for 5 years with no unexpected price hikes</li>
<li>Download speeds of up to 300 Mbps</li>
</ul>
<p>All Verizon 5G Home Internet plans let you add perks for entertainment, shopping and more, all at a great price.</p>
<p><span class="support-footnote">*5G Home and Verizon Home Internet Lite services provided through cellular network; speeds vary due to factors affecting cellular networks.</span></p>
<p><span class="support-footnote">**Consumer data usage is subject to the usage restrictions set forth in Verizon's terms of service; visit: <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/customer-agreement/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p20||||||What is the difference between Verizon 5G Home Internet plans?|https://www.verizon.com/support/customer-agreement/&quot;}">https://www.verizon.com/support/customer-agreement/</a> for more information about 5G Home Internet or Verizon Home Internet Lite or <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/fios-customer-agreement/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p21||||||What is the difference between Verizon 5G Home Internet plans?|https://www.verizon.com/support/fios-customer-agreement/&quot;}">https://www.verizon.com/support/fios-customer-agreement/</a> for Fios internet.</span></p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        Is a Verizon Mobile plan required to get 5G Home?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>No. You can choose to order 5G Home by itself, with no Verizon mobile plan. If you do combine 5G Home with any <a href="/home/internet/5g/plans/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p22||||||Is a Verizon Mobile plan required to get 5G Home?|Verizon mobile phone plan&quot;}">Verizon mobile phone plan</a> (excluding business plans and data-only plans), <a href="/home/internet/5g/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p23||||||Is a Verizon Mobile plan required to get 5G Home?|you may qualify for our Mobile + Home Discount&quot;}">you may qualify for our Mobile + Home Discount</a>. When you have both 5G Home Internet and Verizon mobile phone plan, you'll receive one combined bill.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        Is Verizon 5G Home Internet good for gaming?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Verizon 5G Home Internet offers just what gamers need, with fast download speeds and lower latency to help you level up. To experience the <a href="/home/internet/5g/shop/consumer-guides/gamers-guide-to-the-best-setup/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p24||||||Is Verizon 5G Home Internet good for gaming?|best internet for gaming&quot;}">best internet for gaming</a>, you need a reliable connection that won’t slow you down with a lot of lag or buffering.</p>
<p>While some gamers prefer a wired connection for speed and low latency, Verizon 5G Home Internet offers those features as well as the reliability of Verizon's 5G network. In fact, a reliable high-speed connection is a must not only for high-performance gaming, but also for livestreaming, downloading files and other data-heavy activities like VR gaming. Whether you're playing on a console or a PC or gaming on your <a href="/home/internet/5g/articles/internet-speed-for-gaming/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p25||||||Is Verizon 5G Home Internet good for gaming?|mobile device&quot;}">mobile device</a>, you can be confident in your connection with Verizon 5G Home Internet.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        Can Verizon help cover my early termination fee when I switch?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Yes! If you are stuck in a contract for internet, switch to 5G Home and get up to $500 credit to help cover your early termination fee. <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/5g-home-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p26||||||Can Verizon help cover my early termination fee when I switch?|See details&quot;}">See details</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        Did Verizon acquire Starry? What does that mean for me?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Yes, Starry is now a Verizon company. While current Starry customers will not experience an interruption in their service, you may be eligible for amazing <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/fios-fastest-internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p27||||||Did Verizon acquire Starry? What does that mean for me?|Verizon Fios&quot;}">Verizon Fios</a> and <a href="/home/internet/5g/plans/frontier/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p28||||||Did Verizon acquire Starry? What does that mean for me?|Frontier Fiber&quot;}">Frontier Fiber</a> offers. <a href="#checkAvailability" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p29||||||Did Verizon acquire Starry? What does that mean for me?|Enter your address&quot;}" data-lq-initialized="true">Enter your address</a> to see what <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p30||||||Did Verizon acquire Starry? What does that mean for me?|home internet options&quot;}">home internet options</a> are available in your area.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Verizon participated in ACP, the Affordable Connectivity Program, while the program was active prior to the last fully funded month of April 2024. Verizon now provides reduced-cost internet to eligible new or existing home Internet customers who have qualified for Lifeline, SNAP, WIC, and other assistance programs within 180 days of application or received a Federal Pell Grant within the past year with our <a href="/home/internet/5g/discounts/verizon-forward/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p31||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|Verizon Forward&quot;}">Verizon Forward</a> program. Qualifying customers receive a service discount on their Fios or 5G Home Internet plan price. Existing LTE Home Internet customers may qualify as well.</p>
<p>Verizon knows affordable internet access is important in today's connected world. You may be eligible to save money with other Verizon <a href="/home/internet/5g/discounts/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p32||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|discounts&quot;}">discounts</a>, like:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/featured/first-responders/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p33||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|First responder discount&quot;}">First responder discount</a></li>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/military/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p34||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|Military discount&quot;}">Military discount</a></li>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/featured/nurses/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p35||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|Nurse discount&quot;}">Nurse discount</a></li>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/featured/teachers/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p36||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|Teacher discount&quot;}">Teacher discount</a></li>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/featured/students/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p37||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|Student discount&quot;}">Student discount</a></li>
</ul>
<p>You also can get a discount by <a href="/home/internet/5g/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p38||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|bundling mobile and home&quot;}">bundling mobile and home</a> or signing up for <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/auto-pay-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p39||||||What affordable Verizon Home Internet options are available?|Auto Pay&quot;}">Auto Pay</a>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Whole-Home Wi-Fi is included with <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/5g/" target="_blank" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p40||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|5G Home Ultimate&quot;}">5G Home Ultimate</a><sup>1</sup>, LTE Home Plus<sup>2</sup> or <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/verizon-home-internet-lite/" target="_blank" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p41||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Verizon Home Internet Lite Extra&quot;}">Verizon Home Internet Lite Extra</a> plan. When you have Whole-Home Wi-Fi, you can choose to upgrade to Whole-Home Wi-Fi Plus for $5/month (plus taxes &amp; surcharges).
<br aria-hidden="true">
<br aria-hidden="true">
Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi<sup>3</sup> and Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi Plus<sup>3</sup> include 3 features that help improve Wi-Fi coverage in your home:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/support/verizon-whole-home-wifi-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p42||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Wi-Fi Health Check&quot;}">Wi-Fi Health Check</a> in the My Verizon app to optimize your Wi-Fi network.</li>
<li>Wi-Fi extender(s):<sup>4</sup><ul>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/support/verizon-whole-home-wifi-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p43||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Whole-Home Wi-Fi&quot;}">Whole-Home Wi-Fi</a> gives you 1 optional Wi-Fi extender for better signal strength in hard-to-reach places.</li>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/support/verizon-whole-home-wifi-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p44||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Whole-Home Wi-Fi Plus&quot;}">Whole-Home Wi-Fi Plus</a> gives you a total of 3 Wi-Fi extenders per line. 2 are sent with your order. Add a 3rd if needed after setup.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/home/internet/5g/support/verizon-whole-home-wifi-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p45||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Free router upgrade&quot;}">Free router upgrade</a> after 3 years.<sup>5</sup> Included with the 5G Home Ultimate plan or Verizon Home Internet Lite Extra plan.</li>
</ul>
<p><span class="support-footnote"><sup>1</sup>Also applies to the 5G Home Plus plan if you subscribed between 11/9/23 and 6/18/25.
<br aria-hidden="true">
 <sup>2</sup>New sign-ups for LTE Home plans are no longer available. Existing LTE Home customers can switch LTE Home plans or explore other <a href="/home/internet/5g/digital/nsa/secure/ui/ngd/devices/plans/" target="_blank" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p46||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Verizon Home Internet&quot;}">Verizon Home Internet</a> options.
<br aria-hidden="true">
 <sup>3</sup>Available in select areas.
<br aria-hidden="true">
 <sup>4</sup>Verizon owns the equipment provided with your plan, including the router and Wi-Fi Extender. If your service is disconnected or you change to a plan that does not include some or all of the equipment (such as the Wi-Fi Extender), you must return equipment within 30 days or you'll incur an unreturned equipment fee(s) of up to $300 per unit of equipment (see details in <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/verizon-5g-home-legal/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p47||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Terms of Service&quot;}">Terms of Service</a>). Learn more by visiting our <a href="/home/internet/5g/support/wireless-home-equipment-return-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p48||||||What are Verizon Whole-Home Wi-Fi and Verizon Whole Home Wi-Fi Plus?|Verizon Home Internet (Wireless) equipment return FAQs&quot;}">Verizon Home Internet (Wireless) equipment return FAQs</a>.
<br aria-hidden="true">
 <sup>5</sup>You may be eligible for a no-cost router upgrade once every three years, subject to the following conditions: (1) Your account must be in good standing. (2) You must have maintained a qualifying service plan for the preceding twelve months. (3) You must have used the existing router model for at least three years. Your upgrade eligibility will be displayed after logging into the My Verizon app. Upgraded equipment is subject to availability at the time of your eligibility. Verizon, at its discretion, may provide new or refurbished equipment as part of the upgrade. Verizon reserves the right to alter, limit, modify, or terminate this Router Upgrade Program, including its terms, rules, regulations, benefits, eligibility criteria, or any feature thereof, at any time, with or without prior notice. Such changes are at Verizon's sole discretion.</span></p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
          
  <details>
    <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
      <h3>
        Does Verizon offer backup Wi-Fi?
      </h3>
    </summary>
    <div>
        <p>Yes. <a href="/home/internet/5g/home/internet/wi-fi-backup/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l23|p49||||||Does Verizon offer backup Wi-Fi?|Verizon's Wi-Fi Backup&quot;}">Verizon's Wi-Fi Backup</a> plan is now available. It offers cable or fiber internet customers a reliable solution to stay connected if their primary internet provider has a service disruption or outage.</p>

    </div>
  </details>

        
